9.26.21  11:08 am   As much as you've probably been asked this, it seems like i'm a princess has a slightly more coherent theme/message to it intended than a lot of your other songs, which feel more like general vibes.

     i'm guessing this is because every section starts on the same chord. that's my best assumption as to why this particular song is making you feel this way

     Were you going for a slightly different writing approach on this song?

      my usual approach is to approach the song with a different approach

9.26.21  7:33 am   Is it ok to feel ok sometimes?

      yes

9.26.21  7:04 am   Hahhahahahahhahahahahaahhahahahahahha what Kind of Person are you?

     regular

      I dont know what i should do because my Mom is narcisstic and i can't be myself and im everbody Else but me. Help me Bill 

      maybe it's time to write a play

9.26.21  5:35 am   why are your songs so hypnotizing?

      that's easy, i just try to hypnotize myself with it, and if it doesn't work then i keep fixing it until it does

9.26.21  5:06 am   hi can i be a princess please

     sure

      do i need to sign a form or something

      yes, but, sometimes the whole point of being a princess is being able to skip what you needed to do

9.26.21  3:06 am   when will the next song be out?

      not soon enough for me

9.26.21  2:11 am   do you have a pet volcano

      i'm glad you asked. the answer is no

9.26.21  12:28 am   why did you feel unusual at the airport terminal

      the reason someone might feel unusual in an airport terminal is because they may be in a different city from where they usually spend their day. this makes sense to me

9.26.21  12:23 am   Can u milk a bird

      yes but you have to do it while they're flying

9.26.21  12:19 am   What's your favorite song of yours?

      i would prefer to make a new one to be my favorite

9.26.21  12:10 am   I've written a short story which I think may be legitimately well-crafted, deep, and meaningful... however, I'm terrified to share it with anyone else because I'm afraid that it may actually be just a bunch of bland and meaningless nonsense. What should I do?

      write more. eventually you will share and not-share in every different configuration you've ever dreamed of

9.25.21  10:35 pm   how do I solve the equation of life?

      put everything together

9.25.21  9:12 pm   bill, you know when you realize something that changes how you perceive "reality", and you can't even imagine not realizing what you've found... crazy. when's the last time this has happened to you?

     this happens continuously, at varying levels of strength. i don't know of a reliable method for determining the threshhold for how much counts as 1 occurence

9.25.21  8:36 pm   can you give us an indication as to what direction the video department is heading in?

      FEASIBLE

9.25.21  8:33 pm   What's your process for writing lyrics?

      i make them up, at the same time as i make up the melody and chords

9.25.21  7:41 pm   is it possible to appreciate what you have for more than a little while before adjusting and needing more

      some people claim to be able to do that

9.25.21  7:07 pm   how many attempts did it take for you to do that mic spin in Hello Sexy Pants, at 0:46

      none, that's improvised

9.25.21  6:42 pm   why is 2:17 of 'here comes the sun' your favourite part ofd the video?

      it's actually my least favorite part of the video, when it's actually supposed to be the best. so that message is put there as a diversion, to distract you from how much worse it was than how good it's supposed to be

9.25.21  5:51 pm   What is the cure against loneliness? When it seems that no one supports you or that you are not respected by anyone? 

      this may be the right time to start respecting yourself, 1 brick at a time

9.25.21  5:11 pm   advise on homework?

      if you leave home and do it, it's more fun

9.25.21  5:15 pm   what is paper

      the missing link, between a tree and a computer

9.25.21  4:52 pm   would you say you have a 'target audience'?

     i was going to say no but now that i think about it yes

     if so, what is it?

      everyone

9.25.21  4:48 pm   do you like reading the dictionary

      stressful, to imagine the ongoing battle between what to include and what not to include

      thinking i can do more than i can

9.25.21  6:50 am   how to have fun improvising on piano when my fingers can't keep up with what i want to play and it just sounds like a slow trainwreck instead

      first you'll have to find the fun in simpler things

      some sort of balloon plane

      the video not being good enough

      2 previous universes had a romantic evening together
